Get all cultivar parameters in a model

Source: R/cultivar.R
get_cultivar.Rd

Get all cultivar parameters in a model

get_cultivar(l, alias = TRUE)

Arguments

l

The list of apsimx file

alias

Whether to export alias

Value

A data frame for all cultivar parameters

Examples

wheat <- read_apsimx(system.file("extdata/wheat.json", package = "rapsimng"))
#> Error in readBin(structure(4L, class = c("file", "connection"), conn_id = <pointer: 0x342>),     raw(0), 32768L): can only read from a binary connection
get_cultivar(wheat)
#> Error in r_search_node(l, conds, ele_names, max_depth, 1, all = all): object 'wheat' not found
get_cultivar(wheat, alias = FALSE)
#> Error in r_search_node(l, conds, ele_names, max_depth, 1, all = all): object 'wheat' not found
